                              Mission Statement

   The mission of the Cotton Production and Processing Research Unit is to
     develop and integrate basic knowledge of production and processing
     systems for stripper-harvested cotton to maximize producer returns,
   minimize processing costs, preserve fiber quality, and maintain a clean
                         and safe work environment.

